        "title": "Text 4",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Both Suri and Zane used tape diagrams to solve the problem. Both Zane and Julia determine how many people 1% represents. Kelly scales the ratio to 100 people to write the percent. </p>"
          ]
        }
